1. When employees are recognized frequently, they are more likely to:
Solution : A. Achieve greater performance and results

2. One of the most effective ways to recognize others is to:
Solution : D. Tailor recognition to individuals in a way that makes them feel most valued

3. You can help your teammates recognize each other by:
Solution : D. All of the above

4. When recognizing others, you should:
Solution : C. Find a way to recognize each person on the team
